WEBVTT

00:03:57.843 --> 00:04:00.048
Sasa, hii ni habari njema:

00:04:00.603 --> 00:04:04.885
asilimia 70 ya watu ambao wanasumbuka na msongo wa mawazo hali zao zitaboreka

00:04:04.909 --> 00:04:08.266
kwa kupata tiba na dawa.

00:04:09.458 --> 00:04:11.120
Wakipewa taarifa,

00:04:11.144 --> 00:04:12.851
Nimechukua uamuzi:

00:04:12.875 --> 00:04:15.843
Sitakuwa kimya tena.

00:04:16.740 --> 00:04:18.543
Na baraka za familia yangu,

00:04:18.567 --> 00:04:20.460
Nitasimulia hadithi yetu

00:04:20.484 --> 00:04:23.298
katika matumaini ya kuleta mjadala wa kitaifa.

00:04:24.140 --> 00:04:26.911
Rafiki yangu, Kelly Pierre-Loius, alisema,

00:04:26.935 --> 00:04:29.426
"Kuwa ngangari hutuua."